<span id="freeTextContainer8847167895402395599">An exceptional collection of short stories by Poe covering genres from detective fiction, mystery, adventure and horror. He set new boundaries in his writing and explored themes that hadn&apos;t been really touched on before.</span>
  <span id="freeText8847167895402395599" style="display:none">An exceptional collection of short stories by Poe covering genres from detective fiction, mystery, adventure and horror. He set new boundaries in his writing and explored themes that hadn't been really touched on before.</span>
