<div id="review_2148734755" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2148734755" />
    <a title="Heni Akbar" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/52758981-heni-akbar"><img alt="Heni Akbar" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1593944749p2/52758981.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2148734755?book_show_action=true">Oct 09, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Heni Akbar" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Heni Akbar" href="/user/show/52758981-heni-akbar">Heni Akbar</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/52758981-heni-akbar?shelf=thriller-suspense">thriller-suspense</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/52758981-heni-akbar?shelf=4-stars">4-stars</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2148734755" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5931791882773809468">The Tell-Tale Heart is my favorite, alright. It deserves 5 stars.<br/>However, the sleuth in this anthology is not actually my taste. Murders in the Rue Morgue is (in my opinion) highly overpraised. Well, maybe because it was the pioneer of its time, like The Mystery of Yellow Room.<br/>Still, Poe&apos;s descriptive is beyond comparison. It took me whole concentration to finish one story only. Have difficulty in reading English in this version, highly advanced and so 18th century 😂<br/>Love this piece.</span>
  <span id="freeText5931791882773809468" style="display:none">The Tell-Tale Heart is my favorite, alright. It deserves 5 stars.<br />However, the sleuth in this anthology is not actually my taste. Murders in the Rue Morgue is (in my opinion) highly overpraised. Well, maybe because it was the pioneer of its time, like The Mystery of Yellow Room.<br />Still, Poe's descriptive is beyond comparison. It took me whole concentration to finish one story only. Have difficulty in reading English in this version, highly advanced and so 18th century 😂<br />Love this piece.</span>
  <a data-text-id="5931791882773809468" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


