              <span id="reviewTextContainer2429699574" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12246655838366951993">hehe I just realized that this book was written by EDGAR ALLAN POE. how did I miss that..... anyways, this was a nice short read but none of the stories were scary. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

