<span id="freeTextContainer3273253565882115984">This is the first Edgar Allan Poe I have read after hearing a lot of hype and it really did live up to it. I will certainly be reading more of his. While some of the stories are not now as scary as maybe they once were, they way they are written was fantastic. 5*</span>

          </span>
